      public Signature.Builder key(String key)
      Sets the unique key of this signature.

      When not set explicitly, the default value is Signature.DEFAULT_KEY.

      Parameters:
      key - signature key
      Returns:
      this builder
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if the key is invalid
